timeline
    title Evolution of Disruption-Tolerant Communication
    section Academic Foundations
        2003 : DTN Architecture proposed (Fall, 2003)
            : Epidemic Routing (Vahdat & Becker)
        2007 : RFC 4838 DTN Architecture (Cerf et al.)
            : PRoPHET routing protocol
        2009 : Spray-and-Wait bounded replication
            : Bundle Protocol v6 (RFC 5050)
    section Mobile Money Era
        2007 : M-Pesa launches in Kenya
        2010 : GSMA Mobile Money adoption accelerates
            : USSD becomes dominant payment channel
        2015 : 270+ mobile money services globally
            : NFC offline payment pilots begin
    section Blockchain Infrastructure
        2017 : Helium founded (LoRaWAN DePIN)
        2019 : TON gas model published
            : Filecoin mainnet launch
        2021 : RISC Zero zkVM announced
        2023 : DePIN thesis crystallizes (Messari)
            : BitVM2 bridging proposal
    section Convergence
        2024 : Ekwe Protocol design
            : Multi-radio mesh + incentives + ZK
            : Offline payments + Bitcoin L2 settlement
